# multi-nic-bw-checker

A simple containerized Go app to check max bandwidth across all pod interfaces using `iperf3`.

## ðŸ”§ Build

```bash
make build

```Run server in one pod:


env:
- name: IPERF_MODE
  value: "server"

```Run client in another:


env:
- name: IPERF_MODE
  value: "client"
- name: TARGET_IP
  value: "SERVER_IP"

